(66209, '1463', 'Cottonwood Lakes Walk in Campground', 36.453409, -118.168988, '', '', '', 'https://thedyrt.imgix.net/photo/93422/media/cottonwood-lakes-trailhead-campground_f7320fc950822dbe88225775ebeb6a7d.jpg?ixlib=rb-1.1.0', 'Narrow, single lane road. Only accessible in summer. Accessible by private vehicle only if camping. 52 Campsites.  ACTIVITIES  Camping  ', '', 'From Highway 395, turn west at the stoplight at the center of Lone Pine, and follow Whitney Portal Road for 3 miles. Then turn south onto Horseshoe Meadow Road. The campground is 24 miles from the town of Lone Pine, California.', '', 'http://www.fs.usda.gov/recarea/inyo/specialplaces/recarea/?recid=20692&actid=29', ''),
